@title Images and Videos
@date 2024-04-11

This page explains how to put images and videos in the article.

* Images

You can put an image by writing "@image [/URL/]", where the URL refers to an arbitrary external image resource.  In other words, you can embed any image on the net ino the article.  It also means that you have to store the image anywhere youself and get its permanent URL.

@image https://dbmx.net/harunatsu-bg-lq.jpg

You can set a caption by writing "[caption=[/text/]]" option.  You can also specify the maximum width of the image by writing "[width=[/n/]]" where the number indicates a percent from 1 to 100.

@image https://dbmx.net/harunatsu-bg-lq.jpg [caption=cap] [width=60]

You can juxapose multiple images in columns in the same line.  The image size is automatically adjusted.

@image https://dbmx.net/harunatsu-bg-lq.jpg [caption=cap1] | https://dbmx.net/harunatsu-bg-lq.jpg [caption=cap2]
@image https://dbmx.net/harunatsu-bg-lq.jpg [caption=cap1] | https://dbmx.net/harunatsu-bg-lq.jpg [caption=cap2] | https://dbmx.net/harunatsu-bg-lq.jpg [caption=cap3]
@image https://dbmx.net/harunatsu-bg-lq.jpg [caption=cap1] | https://dbmx.net/harunatsu-bg-lq.jpg [caption=cap2] | https://dbmx.net/harunatsu-bg-lq.jpg [caption=cap3] | https://dbmx.net/harunatsu-bg-lq.jpg [caption=cap4]
@image https://dbmx.net/harunatsu-bg-lq.jpg [caption=cap1] | https://dbmx.net/harunatsu-bg-lq.jpg [caption=cap2] | https://dbmx.net/harunatsu-bg-lq.jpg [caption=cap3] | https://dbmx.net/harunatsu-bg-lq.jpg [caption=cap4] | https://dbmx.net/harunatsu-bg-lq.jpg [caption=cap5]

